title: What Hillary Clinton is saying about wine ice cream, Upstate New York
text: What Hillary Clinton is saying about wine ice cream, Upstate New York Hillary Rodham Clinton Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Rodham Clinton, center, arrives to speak to the United States Hispanic Chamber of Commerce, Thursday, Oct. 15, 2015, in San Antonio. She talked about wine ice cream and how she helped Mercer's Dairy in Central New York grow from a tiny business to one that now exports overseas. Clinton said, "I want to be the small business president." (AP Photo/Eric Gay) (Eric Gay)
